description.narrative: This activity (Framework for nutrition technical assistance (MQSUN)) is a component of Framework for nutrition technical assistance (MQSUN) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £6,240,025. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Health policy and administrative management, Basic nutrition. , with the following implementing partners: Path. The start date is 01-07-2011 and the end date is 07-02-2016.
